<p class="ayah 42-12" id="12" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">To Him (belongs)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَقَالِيدُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) keys</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٲتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the heavens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْأَرْضِ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the earth.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَبْسُطُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He extends</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلرِّزْقَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the provision</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِمَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for whom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَشَآءُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He wills</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَقْدِرُ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and restricts.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, He</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِكُلِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of every</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَىْءٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">thing</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span c