<p class="ayah 42-14" id="14" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَفَرَّقُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they became divided</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">until</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنۢ بَعْدِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">after</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[what]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَآءَهُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">came to them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْعِلْمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the knowledge</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَغْيَۢا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(out of) rivalry,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَيْنَهُمْ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">among them.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَوْلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And if not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَلِمَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(for) a word</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَبَقَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that preceded</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class=