<p class="ayah 42-22" id="22" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَرَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">You will see</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلظَّـٰلِمِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the wrongdoers</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُشْفِقِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">fearful</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَسَبُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they earned,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَاقِعُۢ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will) befall</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهِمْ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[on] them.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَمِلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and do</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">righteous deeds</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span cl