<p class="ayah 42-23" id="23" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">That</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is of) which</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُبَشِّرُ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah gives glad tidings</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِبَادَهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) His slaves -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَمِلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and do</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">righteous deeds.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُل</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَسْــَٔلُكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">I ask you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span cl