<p class="ayah 42-26" id="26" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَسْتَجِيبُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And He answers</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَمِلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and do</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">righteous deeds</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَزِيدُهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and increases (for) them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَضْلِهِۦ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">His Bounty.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْكَـٰفِرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And the disbelievers -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَذَابٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will be) a punishment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَدِيدٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">severe.</span></span></sp