<p class="ayah 42-50" id="50" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُزَوِّجُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He grants them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذُكْرَانًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">males</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِنَـٰثًا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and females;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَجْعَلُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and He makes</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">whom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَشَآءُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He wills</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَقِيمًا‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">barren.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, He</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلِيمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) All-Knower,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَدِيرٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">All-Powerful.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>50<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 42-51" id="51" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">۞ وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِبَشَرٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for any human</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُكَلِّمَهُ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah should speak to him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَحْيًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(by) revelation</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَرَآىِٕ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">behind</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حِجَابٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a veil</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُرْسِلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(by) sending</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَسُولاً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a Messenger</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَيُوحِىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then he reveals</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِإِذْنِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">by His permission</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَشَآءُ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He wills.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, He</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلِىٌّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) Most High,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَكِيمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Most Wise.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>51<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 42-52" id="52" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَكَذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And thus</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْحَيْنَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We have revealed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَيْكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رُوحًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">an inspiration</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">by</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْرِنَا‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Our Command.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُنتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">did you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَدْرِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">know</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْكِتَـٰبُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Book (is)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْإِيمَـٰ