rst rtl" dir="rtl">صِرَٲطٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) path</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّسْتَقِيمٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">straight,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>52<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 42-53" id="53" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">صِرَٲطِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(The) path</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Allah,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the One</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to Whom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(belongs) whatever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٲتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the heavens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and whatever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَرْضِ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the earth.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَلَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Unquestionably!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">To</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">